LanguageData.AS_WeebElf_OdTrait.degreeDatas.0.label: Od Energy Accumulation (Small)
LanguageData.AS_WeebElf_OdTrait.degreeDatas.0.descrip: It has a slightly developed organ called odo, which takes in the mana energy present in the air and converts it into energy, and has the property of storing it inside its body.
LanguageData.AS_WeebElf_OdTrait.degreeDatas.1.label: Od Energy Accumulation (Medium)
LanguageData.AS_WeebElf_OdTrait.degreeDatas.1.descrip: It has a well-developed organ called Od that takes in the mana energy present in the air and converts it into energy, and it has the property of storing it inside its body.
LanguageData.AS_WeebElf_OdTrait.degreeDatas.2.label: Od Energy Accumulation (High)
LanguageData.AS_WeebElf_OdTrait.degreeDatas.2.descrip: It has a well-developed organ called Od that takes in the mana energy present in the air and converts it into energy, and it has the property of storing it inside its body.
LanguageData.AS_WeebElf_OdTrait.degreeDatas.3.label: Od Energy Accumulation (Maximum)
LanguageData.AS_WeebElf_OdTrait.degreeDatas.3.descrip: It has an extremely well-developed organ called Od that takes in the mana energy present in the air and converts it into energy, and has the property of storing it inside its body.
LanguageData.AS_WeebElf_ManaTrait.degreeDatas.0.label: Mana Energy Conversion
LanguageData.AS_WeebElf_ManaTrait.degreeDatas.0.descr: Absorbs mana around you faster, allowing you to efficiently convert it into odo energy within your body.
